      "content": "counselors and hotlines... they don't get it. they just give you scripts. they don't understand that there's no \"navigating\" this. the math literally doesn't work. it's not even a \"difficult time,\" it's a total collapse. once the shame sets in, there's no coming back from it. people don't look at you the same way after you've ruined everything. it feels like the only way to stop the noise and the embarrassment is to just... not be there anymore.",
